  <summary date="2012-02-06T22:02:32Z" status="Introduced in House">Airline First Responder Workplace Fairness Act - Directs the Administrator of the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) to establish an Aviation Rulemaking Committee to develop recommendations for the Administrator to include in a final rule to minimize flight attendant fatigue.

Requires the Committee to comprise aviation safety experts, labor representatives, and industry stakeholders.

Directs the Administrator to issue regulations to minimize flight attendant fatigue.</summary>
